battlec back to ToC or Class ToC

IRI: http://www.semanticweb.org/ko4ebhuk/ontologies/2022/10/tanks#Battle

has super-classes
thing c
is in domain of
battle id dp, battle status dp, has results op, has team op
is in range of
is results of battle op, take part in op
is disjoint with
association c, battle results c, nation c, player c, player statistic c, player statistic on concrete tank c, rapid mode c, siege mode c, tank c, tank type c

avg damage blockeddp back to ToC or Data Property ToC

IRI: http://www.semanticweb.org/ko4ebhuk/ontologies/2022/10/tanks#avgDamageBlocked

Средний заблокированный бронёй урон за бой. Заблокированный бронёй урон — это урон от снарядов (бронебойных, кумулятивных и подкалиберных), которые попали в танк, но не нанесли урона. Значение считается с версии игры 9.0.

has characteristics: functional

has super-properties
player statistic properties dp
has domain
player statistic c
has range
float
